item.description:
FocusBit installation should be a fast and easy process.
1. Download FocusBit Go to Downloads page and get the version for Windows.

2. Extract archive Right-click the archive and select &ldquo;Extract All&rdquo;

Select destination and press &ldquo;Extract&rdquo;

3. Open FocusBit Find file &ldquo;FocusBit.exe&rdquo; and double-click it.
